	The primary agenda to engineer a pofitable solution for any problem is to have a notable business benefits that put the product at a compititive advantage in the market. The GoDeliver deivery solution is primarily useful for ecommerce platforms that are dependent on short distance and less delivery time that usually is needed for grocery, food delivery and other similar platforms.
	On the customer side Godeliver helps to reduces costs mainly in the opertion of automobile fleet by routing the delivery orders in the best route avilable and charging appropriate delivery charges from the consumer. The delivery challenges are especially minimised by the routing mechanism and also provides a way for fleet manager to check if there are any changes to be made by viewing the data visualizations provided from logistics system. Coming from a consumer perspective, the delivery system gives a proper date and time based delivery marked by them giving them a smooth experience.

